snippet.title: Warside - Release Date Announcement
snippet.description:
Attention! The wait is almost over—Warside is officially launching on April 14th! After months of intense development, playtesting, and invaluable community feedback, we’re thrilled to bring you the full release of our turn-based tactics game.  

If you haven’t already, wishlist Warside now to be notified as soon as it goes live!  
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2368300/Warside/ 

Are you ready to choose your Commander and dominate the battlefield? Let us know in the comments, and we’ll see you in the fight!  

Stay sharp, the battle awaits.

Visit us at:
https://firstbreaklabs.com/ 

Follow us on our socials!
DISCORD: https://discord.gg/rcr8JKdBGn
FACEBOOK: https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61561301244150
